388
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:02,080
they'll only play it in private.

389
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:03,150
Boring.

390
00:22:03,150 --> 00:22:05,500
Even sports are ranked and judged.

391
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:08,790
It’s time to rectify the Sports circle in the Feng State.

392
00:22:09,730 --> 00:22:12,590
What ideas do you have, Heroin Cheng?

393
00:22:14,210 --> 00:22:15,510
In my hometown…

394
00:22:16,450 --> 00:22:18,050
Aren't you from the capital?

395
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:20,990
Don't care about these details.

396
00:22:21,520 --> 00:22:23,070
In my hometown,

397
00:22:23,290 --> 00:22:25,230
there is an unparalleled gala

398
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:26,830
which everyone can enjoy.

399
00:22:26,910 --> 00:22:28,700
Show your style on the field,

400
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,930
and display your level in the match.

401
00:22:29,930 --> 00:22:32,130
It soars with passion and fuels dreams.

402
00:22:32,230 --> 00:22:35,250
Its boundless excitement starts from the feet.

403
00:22:35,470 --> 00:22:37,930
