405
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:47,690
Go to the academy first.

406
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:48,760
I'll be there soon.

407
00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:50,420
I want…

408
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:53,660
I know it all.

409
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,710
How dare a martial artist

410
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,460
come to the World's Greatest Academy?

411
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,270
That's right.

412
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:04,330
What are you doing?

413
00:23:04,340 --> 00:23:05,560
You can't bully him.

414
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:07,790
Miss Wen, you're a famous lady.

415
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,370
I advise you

416
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,040
not to associate with this martial artist.

417
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:11,470
You...

418
00:23:11,470 --> 00:23:12,640
Cheng Manyi.

419
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:13,300
Manyi.

420
00:23:13,330 --> 00:23:14,050
Manyi.

421
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,280
What's going on?

422
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:17,390
Cui Jun came to the academy to enroll just now.

423
00:23:17,390 --> 00:23:18,850
But they said he was just a martial artist,

424
00:23:18,850 --> 00:23:20,500
not worthy of high regard.

425
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:22,070
They opposed his enrollment

426
00:23:22,070 --> 00:23:23,000
and bullied him.

427
00:23:23,910 --> 00:23:24,990
How dare you?

428
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:27,480
You even bully an incoming student?

429
00:23:27,510 --> 00:23:29,240
Miss Cheng, you are wrong.

430
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:30,610
We didn't bully him.

431
00:23:30,630 --> 00:23:32,600
We just want to protect

432
00:23:32,630 --> 00:23:35,330
the century-old reputation of the World's Greatest Academy.

433
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:37,520
If you let a martial artist enter without permission,

434
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:39,390
