435
00:23:39,390 --> 00:23:40,850
How can highbrow elegance

436
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,580
be associated with vulgarity?

437
00:23:42,580 --> 00:23:43,510
That makes sense.

438
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:45,300
Such an illegitimate guy can't be our peer.

439
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:47,270
Leave the academy! Leave the academy!

440
00:23:47,270 --> 00:23:47,670
You...

441
00:23:47,670 --> 00:23:49,350
Leave the academy! Leave the academy!

442
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:51,830
