447
00:23:54,970 --> 00:23:55,350
Exactly.

448
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,230
Forget it.

449
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:58,310
I'm a martial artist.

450
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:01,090
My father is just a military officer.

451
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:03,600
I was not worthy of it.

452
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:07,140
I won't trouble you.

453
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:09,380
Cui Jun.

454
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:12,950
Come back with dignity.

455
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:18,200
Martial artists are not the reason for you to be self-abased.

456
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:20,260
"Heaven gave me talent for a reason."

457
00:24:21,180 --> 00:24:23,230
Everyone has their own value.

458
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:25,190
As for you,

459
00:24:26,730 --> 00:24:29,530
you look so pathetic when you show off superiority.

460
00:24:29,530 --> 00:24:32,060
Coming from a family of scholarly tradition?

461
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:34,540
Ladies from noble families?

462
00:24:36,190 --> 00:24:38,510
I'm afraid you can't even compare

463
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,790
to me, a martial artist's daughter.

464
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:40,610
What did you say?

465
00:24:40,610 --> 00:24:42,540
Heaven gave me talent for a reason.

466
00:24:43,610 --> 00:24:44,420
Manyi.

467
00:24:45,150 --> 00:24:45,960
I see.

468
00:24:49,670 --> 00:24:52,270
The essence of education is to nurture people.

469
00:24:52,500 --> 00:24:53,820
It should be people-centered

470
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:55,420
and treat everyone equally.

471
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:57,910
If recruiting martial artists

472
00:24:58,260 --> 00:25:00,390
damages its century-old reputation,

473
00:25:00,590 --> 00:25:01,380
then it

474
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:04,800
doesn't deserve to be called the World's Greatest Academy.

475
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:06,590
You're right, Honey.

476
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:07,640
Brother.

477
00:25:07,910 --> 00:25:08,510
Mr. Wen.

478
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:10,500
