496
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:56,400
Exactly.

497
00:25:56,430 --> 00:25:57,640
Speaking of which,

498
00:25:58,070 --> 00:26:00,830
I have something to announce.

499
00:26:01,910 --> 00:26:02,800
I've decided

500
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:04,720
