503
00:26:10,210 --> 00:26:11,150
Great!

504
00:26:11,170 --> 00:26:12,210
Soccer…

505
00:26:12,630 --> 00:26:13,350
Great!

506
00:26:18,300 --> 00:26:20,180
I just recommended the game to you,

507
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:21,360
