508
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:23,560
Your ability to execute is impressive.

509
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:26,090
First, what you said before,

510
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:28,030
"the comprehensive development"

511
00:26:28,030 --> 00:26:29,970
does make sense.

512
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,000
Good day, Mr. Wen.

513
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:33,640
So, I'm planning to take this opportunity

514
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:36,510
