523
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:56,470
For example…

524
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:57,810
the Eastern Palace?

525
00:26:58,150 --> 00:26:59,480
The one who knows me well

526
00:26:59,940 --> 00:27:01,140
