00:28:56,810 --> 00:29:00,110
Cheng Manyi and Du Yaqin are the team leaders.

577
00:28:56,900 --> 00:29:02,630
[Soccer Match Diagram]

578
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:01,410
You can select your members

579
00:29:01,410 --> 00:29:02,400
by yourselves.

580
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,620
Manyi. Manyi.

581
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:07,570
Cui Jun.

582
00:29:08,810 --> 00:29:09,580
Li Jun.

583
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:11,190
And me, Manyi.

584
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,300
Okay, Feng Qiwu.

585
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:13,400
[Soccer Match Diagram]

586
00:29:15,910 --> 00:29:16,670
I choose...

587
00:29:16,690 --> 00:29:17,660
Mr. Wen.

588
00:29:19,010 --> 00:29:20,650
No, you can't choose him.

589
00:29:20,910 --> 00:29:22,070
Why not?

590
00:29:22,210 --> 00:29:24,930
It's never said that Mr. Wen is not allowed to participate.

591
00:29:24,930 --> 00:29:27,610
Besides, Mr. Wen said himself

592
00:29:27,630 --> 00:29:29,560
that everyone has to participate.

593
00:29:29,570 --> 00:29:32,050
So, doesn't it count?

594
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,850
Of course it does.

595
00:29:40,810 --> 00:29:46,630
[Soccer Match Diagram]

596
00:29:42,430 --> 00:29:43,510
As a teacher,

597
00:29:43,530 --> 00:29:45,120
I should set an example.

598
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:46,900
I'm willing to join the team.

599
00:29:48,630 --> 00:29:50,910
I suddenly realize…

600
00:29:50,910 --> 00:29:51,910
You.

601
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:54,460
The clown is me.

602
00:29:56,770 --> 00:29:57,740
Oh no, Manyi.

603
00:29:58,830 --> 00:30:00,290
We're short of one person.

604
00:30:01,690 --> 00:30:02,620
We need one more.

605
00:30:02,670 --> 00:30:03,620
I'll do it.

606
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:06,970
Manyi, if you don't mind me…

607
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:09,650
It's decided then.

608
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:14,350
[Soccer Match Diagram]

609
00:30:14,450 --> 00:30:15,450
What do you think?

610
00:30:15,460 --> 00:30:16,660
Are you confident?

611
00:30:17,010 --> 00:30:19,210
Sure. We practiced day and night.

612
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:21,030
We'll be able to score in no time.

613
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,950
We must win this battle.

614
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,520
Guys,

615
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,590
Tell me the truth.

616
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,000
What level are you in?

617
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:28,750
I know nothing.

618
00:30:28,780 --> 00:30:30,010
I know a little?

619
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:38,530
Let me calm down first.

620
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:40,120
My head is buzzing.

621
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,750
Fortunately, I've watched countless dramas.

622
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:45,010
I've watched that episode about soccer.

623
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:49,050
Soccer is a team-based, competitive sport

624
00:30:49,080 --> 00:30:50,750
that requires everyone to play their part,

625
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:54,010
with players coordinating through passing, ball control, shooting, and defensive strategies.

626
00:30:54,010 --> 00:30:56,010
There are five players on the field.

627
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:58,490
One will be the goalkeeper.

628
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:01,270
Two will be the forwards,

629
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:03,000
and two will be the backs.

630
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:04,560
Well...

631
00:31:04,570 --> 00:31:08,180
Manyi, what is a goalkeeper?

632
00:31:08,210 --> 00:31:10,240
What do you mean by forwards and backs?

633
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:12,310
To put it simply,

634
00:31:12,430 --> 00:31:14,070
forwards are in charge of attacking,

635
00:31:14,070 --> 00:31:15,190
breaking through defenses, and taking shots,

636
00:31:15,190 --> 00:31:16,410
while defenders focus on marking opponents

637
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:17,710
and covering positions.

638
00:31:17,710 --> 00:31:19,930
We need to be flexible on the field

639
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,910
and change the formation at any time.

640
00:31:21,910 --> 00:31:23,880
If the opponents are aggressive,

641
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,880
the 2-2 formation I just talked about

642
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:27,590
needs to be changed into

643
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:30,420
3-1 formation for defending and counterattacks.

644
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:34,440
Do you understand?

645
00:31:34,450 --> 00:31:35,590
No.

646
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:38,630
I can't teach them.

647
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:41,880
It's just not working at all.

648
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:47,980
That fake is finally going to be kicked out of the academy.

649
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:50,460
I must drink for three days and nights to celebrate.

650
00:31:50,460 --> 00:31:51,640
I told you long ago

651
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:54,230
not to bet on your future.

652
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:56,370
You deserve it.

653
00:31:58,630 --> 00:32:00,230
Mr. Wen, there's no obstacle

654
00:32:00,250 --> 00:32:02,120
between us anymore.

655
00:32:03,300 --> 00:32:03,980
Let's go.

656
00:32:07,570 --> 00:32:08,800
No.

657
00:32:08,820 --> 00:32:09,980
No.

658
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,020
No!

659
00:32:12,050 --> 00:32:14,200
No. No.

660
00:32:14,230 --> 00:32:15,650
No.

661
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:17,530
Manyi.

662
00:32:17,570 --> 00:32:18,380
Manyi?

663
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:23,210
Wen Chenyi, how dare you cheat on me?

664
00:32:23,230 --> 00:32:24,110
What?

665
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,190
I'm sorry.

666
00:32:27,470 --> 00:32:29,350
I might have a fake brain.

667
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,560
But you should leave.

668
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:33,730
We are in different teams now.

669
00:32:33,970 --> 00:32:35,770
We shouldn't talk to each other.

670
00:32:36,490 --> 00:32:38,140
But I'm for you.

671
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:40,580
Then, go to Du Yaqin's team

672
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,320
to be a spy

673
00:32:41,350 --> 00:32:43,240
and get me some information.

674
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:43,710
Wait…

675
00:32:44,370 --> 00:32:45,500
Brother.

676
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:48,860
Brother.

677
00:32:49,190 --> 00:32:50,020
Don't worry.

678
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:52,570
I will keep an eye on Manyi for you.

679
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,460
Keep an eye?

680
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:57,980
After all, there is a royal member

681
00:32:58,330 --> 00:33:00,280
and a childhood friend of hers on our team.

682
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:02,130
She's surrounded by wolves.

683
00:33:02,150 --> 00:33:04,150
They are all strong rivals of yours.

684
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:06,750
The marriage of my brother and sister-in-law

685
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,630
is in danger.

686
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:09,160
You can be the back.

687
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:10,110
You run fast.

688
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:13,200
Manyi did all this for me.

689
00:33:13,270 --> 00:33:14,400
If we lose,

690
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,900
I'll drop out with you.

691
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:20,820
A gentleman dies for his confidant.

692
00:33:20,820 --> 00:33:22,470
I'm willing to stand together

693
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:23,310
with you.

694
00:33:24,170 --> 00:33:26,110
Good friends. You're both loyal.

695
00:33:26,570 --> 00:33:29,160
We'll face it together if we lose,

696
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:31,190
and celebrate together if we win.

